last_episode_to_air.overview: The community gather to farewell a friend while Hazel questions whether Arcadia Heights is truly home. Ash and Kam make a decision that will rock the Jafari's world.

name: The Heights
overview: A groundbreaking serial about a community trying to protect its way of life, while under the constant threat of gentrification and the social stratification of its neighbourhood.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: The residents of Arcadia Towers are left reeling after an abandoned baby is discovered. Hazel is stunned when her estranged son Ryan returns from London. Leonie struggles with Mich’s desire to move in with his dad.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Following Shannon being identified as the abandoned baby’s mother, Hazel and Ryan are desperate for answers. Sabine navigates her first day at Arcadia High. Sully invites Ash to dinner with Iris – with disastrous consequences.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Ryan and Hazel race to find Shannon as social services gets involved. A smitten Sully buys Ash's affection. Pav and Claudia are unable to deny their attraction. Leonie reluctantly allows Mich to move into the towers.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Pav and Claudia's date is gate-crashed. Sully makes a drunken move on Ash. Ryan and Hazel reopen old wounds as they finally decide what to do with Patch.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Ash struggles on the job with Mark following a night of partying, and Ryan and Hazel discover that their inheritance isn't all that it seems.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Pav and Claudia's second date gets ruined by their kids, Kam lands himself and Iris in trouble with the police. Hazel refuses to cancel her Mahjong game on account of Patch, and the community come together to make it happen.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: An accident at home makes Renee see red over the unfinished renovations. Claudia struggles to reconcile with Sabine following her discovery that she's sexually active. Iris learns the truth behind Kam's business antics.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Mark feels the pressure when Renee insists they get a loan to finish the house renovations. Ash enjoys the high life when he meets up with Tyler and his friends. Kam impresses Iris with his entrepreneurial skills.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Sully has a disastrous first day at his teaching practical and Claudia establishes some ground rules around Sabine and Dane's relationship.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Mark becomes further entangled in his web of lies when Renee makes a troubling discovery. Hazel questions her ability to mother when Patch falls ill. Ash is unsettled by Tyler's interest in him.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Ryan and Ana's friendship grows into something more. Claudia's confronted by a gift Sabine receives. Ash becomes disillusioned with Tyler's world and Leonie shuts down Mich's questions about their Aboriginal heritage.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Mich is determined to explore his Aboriginal heritage. Ash disappoints Kam, whilst Ryan has a sweet surprise for Ana. Mark and Renee struggle in the bedroom as Pav and Claudia heat up.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Bruce finally opens up to Leonie about her Indigenous mother, Pav and Claudia are bad at being friends with benefits and Iris decides to find Sully a boyfriend.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Pav's new romance with Claudia becomes complicated. Sully loses in love but has a win at school. Ryan and Ana grow closer while preparing the pub for its imminent relaunch.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: Ana and Ryan finally get together, only to be confronted by an unexpected third wheel. Renee is horrified when Mark confesses to his gambling addiction. Claudia and Pav struggle to keep their romance secret.

episodes.name: Episode 16
episodes.overview: Ryan uses the pub's launch to avoid talking to Lottie while Ana's unsure where she stands after Lottie's arrival. Renee tells Mark he needs to get help with his gambling addiction.

episodes.name: Episode 17
episodes.overview: Ryan learns why Lottie declined his marriage proposal. Renee decides to go back to work in order to pay Mark's debt. Sabine struggles with her heartache while Sully and Fraser take their relationship to the next level.

episodes.name: Episode 18
episodes.overview: Dane shares an intimate photo of Sabine. Ryan encourages Ana to give Evan a chance. The Jafaris give Kam a special gift. Claudia panics when Pav delivers on her birthday.

episodes.name: Episode 19
episodes.overview: Kam nearly messes up his chances at getting the scholarship but Iris encourages him to keep fighting. Claudia learns of Sabine's photo and the harassment. Mark makes Renee realise that her anger is affecting their family.

episodes.name: Episode 20
episodes.overview: Kam lies to his family. Mich receives his grandmother's death certificate, leading Leonie to make a shock discovery. Sully is growing tired of being second fiddle and Lottie treats Ryan to a romantic evening.

episodes.name: Episode 21
episodes.overview: A chance encounter forces Leonie to face up to her past. Pav is frustrated by Claudia's reluctance to admit they're in a relationship. Ana realises that Lottie is here to stay but can she let Ryan go?

episodes.name: Episode 22
episodes.overview: Leonie comes into contact with a long lost relative she was told was dead. Mark's resolve is tested when he's handed a bunch of money. Sully's secret is blown.

episodes.name: Episode 23
episodes.overview: Sully and Ash grow closer as Sully navigates the wrath of Iris. Renee and Leonie fight over Renee's spending habits. Ryan realizes the sacrifice Lottie is making by staying in Arcadia for him.

episodes.name: Episode 24
episodes.overview: Mark attempts to win back Renee's favour on Frankie's birthday. Sully realises he can no longer stand playing second fiddle. Leonie makes a drastic decision when she realises work is getting in the way of family.

episodes.name: Episode 25
episodes.overview: Ash is confronted when Tyler pressures him. Pav's hurt when he catches Claudia lying about his job to her colleagues. Ana realises she's misjudged Evan. Sully wonders whether he's cut out to be a teacher.

episodes.name: Episode 26
episodes.overview: Tragedy hits Arcadia towers. Ash struggles with his sexuality. Sabine gets revenge on the boys who have been harassing her with an outrageous piece of public art.

episodes.name: Episode 27
episodes.overview: Hazel and Ryan are shocked when a ghost from the past turns up in Arcadia. Ana and Ryan are forced to face their feelings for each other. Mark attempts to get the spark back into his relationship with Renee.

episodes.name: Episode 28
episodes.overview: Shannon returns with a new man and a new lease on life. Renee struggles to face the reality of her new life without Mark. Leonie finds inspiration for a career change in the most unlikely of places.

episodes.name: Episode 29
episodes.overview: Ryan and Shannon struggle with the decision of whether to leave Arcadia. Kam finds out his results from Embleton. Mark and Renee clash over telling the kids about their decision.

episodes.name: Episode 30
episodes.overview: Hazel faces losing both her children again but won't let them go without a fight. Renee hides a huge secret from Mark and Patch's father is revealed in this shocking finale.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: The revelation that Pav is Patch's father reverberates across Arcadia. It drives Mich to make a mistake he'll regret, Shannon towards old habits, and Claudia to question her relationship with Pav.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: The Murphys fight for Patch after he's removed by Child Services. Ash strives to become his own boss and Amira's birthday forces Mich and Sabine to paste over their post-kiss awkwardness.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Pav and Claudia are forced to face some hard truths about their relationship, while Evan puts his foot in it with Ana. Ash meets a fiery Driive customer, and Uncle Max gets some troubling news.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Hazel lets Shannon watch Patch with frightening consequences. Uncle Max gets Leonie involved in a legal matter as he confronts his mortality. Kam navigates his first day at Embleton while Sully helps Ana at uni.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Shannon searches for a job that will impress Child Services while Leonie struggles to connect with her new client. Mark's battle to hide his homelessness from Renee becomes harder as she contemplates her pregnancy.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: A surprise visit from Child Services threatens to expose Hazel's deceit. Uncle Max seeks reconciliation while urging Mich to address his anger. Mark and Renee realise they need to step up as parents.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Ana's relationship with Evan is thrown off balance when she learns Ryan is dating again. Laila ropes Sully into tutoring her while Ash remains uneasy around. Claudia is confronted by a former patient.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: The residents of Arcadia Heights come together to celebrate Vietnamese New Year and the 20-year anniversary of Iris' store. Hamid pushes Ash to date Helena and Claudia struggles in the wake of her robbery.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: News spreads of a threat to the Towers. Kam's lies about Dane are exposed, driving Sabine to tell Amira the truth about Mich. A dance class leads to a series of revelations from Renee, Claudia, and Leonie.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Pav reconsiders his future when his compensation claim disappoints. Mark realises that making amends will require a sacrifice. An ostracised Sabine faces the consequences of her fallout. Shannon struggles in her new role.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Assumptions about Sabine's physical abilities intrude upon rehearsals. Evan lays out his views on Ana's commitment. Mark delivers big news to Renee as Leonie and Erika grow closer following a break-in.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: When Leonie hosts a farewell dinner for Mark, politics, romance, and secrets are revealed. Meanwhile, Hamid catches an intimate moment between Ash and Sully.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Fearing Mark's relapse, Renee searches for answers as Leonie struggles after kissing a woman. Jamie resurfaces and seeks Claudia's forgiveness while Iris continues to interfere in Sully's professional life.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Uncle Max strives to ignite the residents of Arcadia in the lead up to the election. Leonie fights to keep Big Mike out of prison. Sully confronts his fear of public speaking in an attempt to help the Community Centre.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: Shannon's feelings for Pav grow while Ryan foolishly attempts to prove his devotion to Amber. An unexpected encounter with Juliana results in Kam clashing with Hamid, and Sabine reaches breaking point.

episodes.name: Episode 16
episodes.overview: A nasty turn in the campaign forces Kam to decide where he stands as Arcadia votes. Uncle Max and Hazel endeavour to get Reza over the line and Iris sees Pav's cafe as a threat. Mich and Sabine restore their friendship.

episodes.name: Episode 17
episodes.overview: Uncle Max's fight to protect the Towers is put at risk when a ghost from his past resurfaces. Ash's attempts to buoy Helena push them closer. Shannon is misguided in her attempt to get between Claudia and Pav.

episodes.name: Episode 18
episodes.overview: A fed-up Kat drives Mich and Pav to a showdown. Sully fears Laila is being groomed by an online predator and a close call for Ash drives him to double down in his deception of Helena.

episodes.name: Episode 19
episodes.overview: Kam makes a decision that could jeopardise his future at Embleton while Uncle Max tries to reconcile with his brother. After quitting the play, Sabine is forced to confront her views on her disability.

episodes.name: Episode 20
episodes.overview: Ash decides to stop living a lie and is finally honest with Helena. Rose introduces Kam to the concept of fun while Shannon opens up to Pav about her true feelings.

episodes.name: Episode 21
episodes.overview: Mich is hit with a realisation that could threaten his friendship with Sabine. Rose challenges Kam to a game. After Pav's rejection Shannon looks to use Patch to punish him. Ryan tries to cheer up Ana.

episodes.name: Episode 22
episodes.overview: Shannon's looming sentencing threatens to separate her from Patch and tear the Murphys apart. Sabine considers her feelings for Mich and Claudia considers her role in Jamie's drug addiction.

episodes.name: Episode 23
episodes.overview: Juliana calls a public meeting and the Tower residents kick into action, but victory is not certain. Hamid discovers Kam's lies while Claudia and Renee's opposing views cause a rift in their friendship.

episodes.name: Episode 24
episodes.overview: A surprise cameo during the school play reignites passions between Pav and Claudia while Rose's disappointment drives Kam to act out. Uncle Max prepares for the inevitable, breaking Hazel's heart.

episodes.name: Episode 25
episodes.overview: Kam's guilt over Huang Fu drives him to take drastic actions. Sully discovers a secret about Iris as things heat up between Leonie and Erika. Pav finds an unexpected hurdle to relaunching his relationship with Claudia.

episodes.name: Episode 26
episodes.overview: Mich is challenged by Sabine's opinion of him. Renee discovers Frankie's getting bullied. Claudia plays dirty in order to keep the safe injecting room. Kam publicly embarrasses himself to get Rose back.

episodes.name: Episode 27
episodes.overview: A blast from the past forces Ash to rethink some choices he's made as Shannon battles people's reconceptions. Following a double date, Ana returns home to a horrible surprise.

episodes.name: Episode 28
episodes.overview: The Jafari home is ripped apart when Hamid makes a tough decision. Ana questions her feelings after her return home is thwarted. The Murphy's unite to brew beer for the pub while the wedge between Claudia and Renee grows.

episodes.name: Episode 29
episodes.overview: The Tower residents band together to bring Ana home after tragedy strikes. Shannon encourages Hazel and Uncle Max to take a break while Evan makes a life-changing realisation.

episodes.name: Episode 30
episodes.overview: The community gather to farewell a friend while Hazel questions whether Arcadia Heights is truly home. Ash and Kam make a decision that will rock the Jafari's world.
